Searing touch
Discworld ritual help
Searing touch

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Searing touch -- Makes an enemies armour burn with the power of your God
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Searing Touch, when performed on an enemy, causes one piece of armour chosen by your God to
become extremely hot. This piece of armour will be chosen from the top most layer of what
the target is wearing. The target will continue to receive severe burns until the armour is taken
off.  You require a holy amulet and a holy symbol to ask this request of your God.
.EP
